title: Absolute Dominion
description: Absolute Dominion Manhwa Absolute Reign, Absolute Monarch, 절대군림 “I shall devour this Jianghu!” Says a mysterious son of the fruit merchant, holding the Monarch Sword in his left hand, and the Hell Blade on his right. Possessing not only eloquence but even an overwhelming martial prowess, what could be his ultimate goal? The delightful journey of the twenty year old youth, ‘ Jeok Leegeon’, who dreams of dominating the martial world, begins!
